description:
After Anne’s unveiling, Sister Davis was feeling pretty good about herself. Being the
wife of the Seed Bearer was a special thrill and honor - and everyone knew it. The
handsome man was eager to fill her with his seed and have her carry his many
offspring. The Seed Bearer knew this was something all Mormon girls must understand,
so he demanded Anne be present. There’s nothing more sacred than taking a
husband’s seed again and again.
title: Sister Davis Family Breeding
